title: Tuesday Pt2: Biggest takeaways from week-1; Power Rankings; Nate Boyer
itunes:title: Tuesday Pt2: Biggest takeaways from week-1; Power Rankings; Nate Boyer
description:
Part Two of the Good Morning Football Podcast starts with hosts Jamie Erdahl, Kyle Brandt, Peter Schrager, and Super Bowl Champion Jason McCourty sharing their biggest takeaway from week-1. Next, they’re joined by Dan Hanzus and he talks about burying the Cowboys in his latest power rankings, the good signs coming out of Tampa Bay, and the concerns about the Packers offense. Later, they’re joined by former NFL player and United States Army Green Beret Nate Boyer and he talks about his new movie coming out tomorrow called MVP. Part two of the podcast finishes up with everyone sharing their favorite images from week-1.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
